actions.message:
Anyone who abuses/breaks the following rules will be muted/kicked/banned from the server depending on the severity of the offense
 In this server we do not tolerate spamming this includes text and voice.

 Please be nice and friendly to the community, we do not like bad behaviour.

 Moderation is final.  If you wish to appeal regarding your moderation please contact a member of staff.

 Swearing is not allowed or bypassing chat filter that is deemed to be a swear and is inappropriate is not allowed.
 NSFW content is not allowed

 Any abuse of the server (ex: Raiding) is not allowed, this is a kick. However if you do raid this or a server with more than 450 members, you will be banned.

 Only mention people if you have to. Mentioning people as a means of annoying them is grounds for being kicked from the discord. (e.g. Mentioning a bunch of people and then deleting your message, and pinging newcomers)
 Alternate accounts joined here are not allowed. (Excludes Admins and above)

 Please send emoji reactions in a polite way, do not send these for hate, abuse, disrespect or anything that is may cause harm, this will result in a warn.

 Sending personal information of anyone is not allowed. Please protect each of our privacy.

 Do not beg, sell and advertise here, we do not want anyone being scammed.
 Do not play any 2 music at the same time, audios are in the maximum of 6 minutes in time length.

 Do not cause or have an intention of spamming our Server Logs.

 Only English must be spoken.
